text: List of ICC Cricket World Cup Winners - Men & Women Tournaments Cricket World Cup is one of the biggest sports events held across the world and is organised by the International Cricket Council (ICC) after an interval of every four years. Given below is the World Cup Winners list for the Men & Women’s Cricket world cut for 50 and 20 overs.
